OL,4,CGolden Globes organisers expels
OL,5,Cex-president over Black Lives Matter
OL,6,Cemail
OL,7, The organisation behind Hollywood's
OL,8, Golden Globe Awards has expelled its
OL,9, former president over an article he
OL,10, shared about Black Lives Matter.
OL,12,FPhilip Berk, 88, had been a member of
OL,13,Fthe Hollywood Foreign Press Association
OL,14,F(HFPA) for 44 years and its president
OL,15,Ffor eight years.
OL,17,FIn a group email with HFPA members,
OL,18,FBerk reportedly shared an article that
OL,19,Fdescribed BLM as a "racist hate group".
